messages.speech:
Lactation Rooms are available in the East Campus Health Service Center (E2232) and in the West Campus 1st Floor Bathroom located by Stairwell E (W1203) near the coffee shop and bookstore.  This space includes a comfortable chair, table and electrical outlet as well as a diaper changing station.

The room on West Campus requires a key.  Contact information for the key safe access code is:

    Human Resources 651-779-5804
    The Connection  651-779-3358
    Campus Safety 651-747-4000 (For After Hours)
